    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Chandeliers having a height-adjustable central burner which can be lowered to increase illumination when necessary, as at dinner or for reading.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000083267/Myers, Gaslighting in America (1978)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Arañas que tienen un mechero central de altura regulable el que puede bajar o aumentar la iluminación cuando es necesario, como durante la comida o para leer.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
